<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-01-27T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-01-27T13:00:00-05:00" n="305" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d305">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">741.9111/30: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Winant</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-01-27T19:00:00+01:00">January
                                    27, 1942—7 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received January 27—1:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>386. Your 303, January 26, 9 p.m. The Embassy has informed the Foreign
                            Office today both orally and by formal note of the stipulations set
                            forth in your telegram regarding the Anglo-Soviet-Iranian treaty.</p>
                        <p>The Foreign Office received a telegram from Tehran this morning stating
                            that the treaty passed its second reading yesterday and is to go into
                            effect January 29.<note n="54" xml:id="d305fn54">For text of Treaty of
                                Alliance between the United Kingdom, the Soviet Union, and Iran,
                                signed at Tehran, January 29, 1942, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, March 21, 1942, p. 249.</note>
                        </p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Winant</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>